title: Behind the scenes on Joanne Froggatt's latest drama
text:
Joanne Froggatt is the girl from Littlebeck in North Yorkshire who's attracted worldwide attention for her role in ITV's Downton Abbey - picking up a Golden Globe Award on the way.
She has been a familiar face on our screens for nearly twenty years, and as Downton draws to a close this year, Joanne's moving onto her next project 'Dark Angel' - about serial killer Mary Ann Cotton. Daniel Harris caught up with her on the set.
